Package server.facade

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IAIFacade  
    IInnerGameFacade
    Handles the requests from the server that have to do with the Inner functionality of the game, but not the Move commands.
    IMovesFacade
    Handles the requests from the server that have to do with the move commands.
    IOuterGameFacade
    Handles the requests from the server that have to do with the outer functionality of the game.
    IUserFacade
    Handles the requests from the server that have to do with the user interaction with the client.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MockInnerGameFacade
    stores canned responses for inner game
    MockMovesFacade
    facade to talk to the mockMoves part of the server
    MockOuterGameFacade
    facde to talk execute commands on the outergame server
    MockUserFacade
    gets the canned response for logging in
    ServerAIFacade  
    ServerInnerGameFacade
    gets repsonse from specific games
    ServerMovesFacade
    creates moves commands and calles execute on them
    ServerOuterGameFacade
    gets and creates games and allowing to join game
    ServerUserFacade
    used for logging in and registering
